", "xref": {"fqname": "constants.None", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "documentation": ["Creates a new parser.\n\n```\nparam fields\n\nColumn types, in order of occurrence.\n```\n"]}, {"name": "tsv.helper.Parser.parse_record", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "record", "type": {"name": "Tuple", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Tuple", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "bytes", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bytes", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, {"name": "...", "xref": null, "params": null}]}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "Tuple", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Tuple", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, {"name": "...", "xref": null, "params": null}]}, "documentation": ["Parses a tuple of byte arrays representing a TSV record into a tuple of Python objects.\n\n```\nparam record\n\nA tuple of  objects, in which each tuple element corresponds to a field.\n\nreturns\n\nA tuple of Python objects, corresponding to a TSV record.\n```\n"]}, {"name": "tsv.helper.Parser.parse_line", "asynchronous": false, "params": [{"name": "self", "type": null, "default": null}, {"name": "line", "type": {"name": "bytes", "xref": {"fqname": "functions.bytes", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, "default": null}], "returns": {"name": "Tuple", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Tuple", "project": "--std--"}, "params": [{"name": "Any", "xref": {"fqname": "typing.Any", "project": "--std--"}, "params": null}, {"name": "...", "xref": null, "params": null}]}, "documentation": ["Parses a line representing a TSV record into a tuple of Python objects.\n\nEquivalent to\n`` `\nreturn self.parse_record(tuple(line.split(b\"\\t\")))\n` ``\n\n```\nparam line\n\nA  object of character data, corresponding to a full record in TSV.\n\nreturns\n\nA tuple of Python objects, corresponding to a TSV record.\n```\n"]}, {"name": "tsv.helper.Parser.par